main event: On 30 August 1954, witnesses observed a white or silver circle with 5 lights moving in a circular motion.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 3 to 4 minutes., The object made no sound., The lights were observed at a 60-degree elevation and 75-degree azimuth., The object disappeared without a trail., The source of the observation was a civilian.
sighted object: white or silver circle with 5 lights
